ygData.messageBody:
I'm no master at this game but I would suggest you get a mino axe first if
you dont already have one. Then save up for banded armor and then get the
toma. I dont know where you hunt for cash but im levl 11 and it would take
me ages to get 100-200pp in a derv camp and they give pp loot sometimes. If
you get the armor you can wack larger mobs thus gettin larger loot.

Im trying to get a lev 11-14 team together on Solusk Ro to go hunt in the
gorge of king xorbb. I tried to solo some stuff there but it wasnt worth
it.

If you are interested in joining the hunt gimme a tell.
I'll be on from 5.30 CET

Vashi, (hmm any swedes on solusek?)
